OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in child sexual exploitation
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FA man accused of being involved in
OL,8,Fgroup that sexually exploited three
OL,9,Fgirls in Rhyl has said he had only
OL,10,Fknown one of the victims "a few days"
OL,11,Fbefore the alleged offending occurred.
OL,13,FMohammed Arshad, 35, of Trellewelyn
OL,14,FRoad, Rhyl, pleaded not guilty to four
OL,15,Fcounts of rape, three counts of sexual
OL,16,Fassault and three counts of inciting a
OL,17,Fchild aged under 16 to engage in
OL,18,Fsexual activity.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
