PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781179881
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in child sexual exploitation
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHe also is accused of six offences
OL,8,Funder Section 1 and 2 of the Modern
OL,9,FSlavery Act, conspiracy to supply
OL,10,FClass A and Class B drugs, possession
OL,11,Fof a firearm, and breach of a Slavery
OL,12,Fand Trafficking Risk Order (STRO).
OL,14,FIt is the prosecution's case that the
OL,15,Fgirls, aged 16 and under, were
OL,16,Ftargeted by Mustafa Iqbal, Mohamed
OL,17,FArshad, Ziaullah Badshah and Jaswinder
OL,18,FSingh, who acted as a grooming gang
OL,19,Fand used the teens as "sexual
OL,20,Fplaythings", plying them with drink
OL,21,Fand drugs before sexually abusing them.
OL,26,@{D@WOU|D@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
