PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781179881
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in child sexual exploitation
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FA fifth defendant, Sarah Gray from
OL,8,FFlintshire is charged with Perverting
OL,9,Fthe course of justice, assisting an
OL,10,Foffender, conspiracy to supply cocaine
OL,11,Fto another, and conspiracy to supply
OL,12,Fcannabis to another.
OL,14,FThe prosecution case is that she is
OL,15,Faccused of allowing Iqbal to use her
OL,16,Fhome as a safe house to sexually
OL,17,Fexploit Child A. It was also claimed
OL,18,Fshe washed bedding following an
OL,19,Fallegation of rape. She denies the
OL,20,Fallegations.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
