FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781179881
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in child sexual exploitation
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FAll the defendants deny all the
OL,8,Fcharges against them.
OL,10,FGiving evidence in court on Wednesday
OL,11,F(10 June), defendant Mohammed Arshad
OL,12,Ftold the court that he first met two
OL,13,Fof the teenage girls when he went to
OL,14,Fvisit his friend Mr Iqbal at his home.
OL,16,FHe said that he found allegations that
OL,17,Fhe had sexual contact on one occasion
OL,18,Fwith one of the girls on part of the
OL,19,Fpremises of his family business "mind-
OL,20,Fboggling".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781179881
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in child sexual exploitation
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHe also said that he was bound to be
OL,8,Fseen by others if such an act had
OL,9,Ftaken place there - adding that if the
OL,10,Faccusation had come earlier he could
OL,11,Fhave used his own or even the
OL,12,Fcouncil's CCTV to disprove it.
OL,14,FThe court heard from Mr Arshad that
OL,15,Fone of the girls assured him she was
OL,16,F17 - and that "if I had known she was
OL,17,F15 I would never have let her into my
OL,18,Fcar...I have been stupid and now I'm
OL,19,Fhere".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781179881
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in child sexual exploitation
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHe continued: "I was stupid and a bit
OL,8,Fflattered - it was wrong but she was
OL,9,Fconstantly flirting with me, asked me
OL,10,Fif I wanted a drink - I'd only known
OL,11,Fher for a few days."
OL,13,FDuring questioning he told his
OL,14,Fcounsel, Grahame James he "kissed her
OL,15,Fin the car, yes" - but added that
OL,16,Fthere had been no sexual contact apart
OL,17,Ffrom that.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
