FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1781179881
OL,3,CMan denies knowing age of alleged
OL,4,Cvictim in child sexual exploitation
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FMr Arshad has pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fall charges alleged against him,
OL,9,Fincluding rape and offences under the
OL,10,FModern Slavery Act.
OL,12,FSpeaking on 10 June, Alexandra Felix
OL,13,FKC - the defence counsel for Mustafa
OL,14,FIqbal, from Rhyl - told the court that
OL,15,Fher client would not be giving
OL,16,Fevidence as part of that defence. He
OL,17,Fhas pleaded not guilty to all charges,
OL,18,Fincluding three of rape.
OL,20,FThe case continues.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/7
